{"tid":1449643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:23.000Z","uid":216800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"57f19e834317ea51e57b2874116232323e0d3323","tid":1449643,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb7783dde159fb7ccd36e3ea3b1f5624bb81b46","tid":1449643,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14083de3f7d7081000110ecd5e34e354bc7e37b5","tid":1449643,"uid":202238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f59cda2d1c424cd272adbb7a8b66eefad2fab31c","tid":1449643,"uid":228175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81a5b33ba573865ab04e8e5c0edfcd61efafff97","tid":1449643,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14083de3f7d7081000110ecd5e34e354bc7e37b5","tid":1449643,"uid":202238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"謝推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521f91f53